Summary: Objects were first in a triangle form coming from ocean. Broke formation and proceeded east in a straight line due east.
divs: sighting detailsmy wife first spotted objects in a triangle formation while parking her car. (same location as past (2) sightings several years ago). ran into our house to get husband. both went outside in street with neighbour to observe objects break triangle formation and proceed slowly east one after the other quite slowly. each object was seperated from the following object behind it by approx. 1 mile. the first thing we thought is, "here they are again". all witnesses were pretty amazed but this sighting wasn't as dramatic as the feb. 27th \ march 2nd, 2008 sightings that were located in the exact same airspace. all objects departed beyond the horizon due east.
